From: Ben Browning <bbrownin@redhat.com>
Date: Sun, 14 Jun 2026 16:58:58 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] [Frontend] Simplify Gemma4 bare-thought parser and
 deduplicate test tokenizer factories

Extract shared _make_tokenizer(sequence) to replace three copy-pasted
mock tokenizer factories and one inline copy. Flatten the channel-opener
injection condition in Gemma4Parser._preprocess_feed for clarity.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>

Signed-off-by: Ben Browning <bbrownin@redhat.com>
